{"tid":809242,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位手足新劇 中學聖日記！","createTime":"2018-09-07T04:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T07:06:28.000Z","uid":2169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f19ed302b636459c4d6a3f13d4660890701fca7a","tid":809242,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:20:04.000Z","msg":"25歲人氣女星有村架純將演出TBS電視台10月首播新劇《中學聖日記》，劇集改編自同名漫畫，有村架純飾演嘅末永聖係一位女教師，原本有由町田啟太飾演嘅未婚夫，卻與15歲男學生黑岩晶發展一段禁斷之戀，男學生由19歲新人岡田健史演出<br />\n《中學聖日記》已公開預告片同拍攝花絮，岡田健史喺班上向後跌，對扶自己嘅老師有村架純有微妙感覺，佢又大膽問老師「喜歡自己咩地方」，亦有一場佢掌摑有村嘅場面。另一方面，又見到町田啟太送上戒指向有村求婚，同埋町田啟太從後擁抱傷心注喊緊嘅有村。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180905/large/1536137932_637a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180905%2Flarge%2F1536137932_637a.jpg&h=5c7ba094&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180905/large/1536137493_a71e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180905%2Flarge%2F1536137493_a71e.jpg&h=00eace2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d70305bed54c3372eb59eac3fde646703e4e9b2b","tid":809242,"uid":2169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:20:53.000Z","msg":"請各位手足G持黎緊有村架純新劇 中學聖日記！<br />\n<br />\n食左我幾隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bfac3c5ba36ddfc905fc475c26bf0f287cf9141","tid":809242,"uid":171754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:21:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"145f32ef3377e9b760cc9edca397bf404fb93bc9","tid":809242,"uid":2169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7bfac3c5ba36ddfc905fc475c26bf0f287cf9141","tid":809242,"uid":171754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:21:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T04:25:52.000Z","msg":"這不是麻友post"},{"pid":"f19d7dd80e11c3428b16bb28f45901d4b37b0785","tid